G.A.-H., Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
K.G.G., Defendant,
and
A.M., Defendant-Appellant,
and
GEM Ambulance, LLC, Defendant-Appellant,
and
Lakewood S.C. United, Defendant,
and
Monmouth Ocean Soccer Association a/k/a MOSA, Jersey Shore Boca, and Jersey Shore Boca JR FC League, Defendants. M-837/838 September Term 2018
081545 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 4, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion of the New Jersey Association for Justice for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-838) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion of the New Jersey Association for Justice for reconsideration of the Court's orders denying the motion for an extension of time within which to file an amicus curiae brief and for leave to appear as amicus curiae (M-837) is denied.
